			Company Description 
		


                Azure Power Global Ltd. is a holding company, which engages in the development, production, and sale of solar energy. The company was founded by Harkanwal Singh Wadhwa and Inderpreet Singh Wadhwa in 2008 and is headquartered in New Delhi, India.
            




